'''Yasoshima Festival''' (八十島祭, やそしままつり / やそじままつり / やそじまのまつり) was a ritual performed at {{ill|Naniwazu|ja|難波津}} as part of the '''Imperial enthronement ceremonies''' from the '''Heian period''' to the '''Kamakura period'''. It has since been discontinued.{{Sfn|八十島祭（国史）}}
